---
// Speed is the whole game — compact two-column stat + live speed comparison.
---
<section class="problem section" aria-labelledby="problem-h">
  <div class="container problem-grid">
    <div class="problem-copy">
      <p class="kicker reveal">The leak in your funnel</p>
      <h2 id="problem-h" class="problem-h reveal">
        <span class="big" data-count data-to="65" data-suffix="%">65%</span>
        of businesses take over a day to answer a DM.
      </h2>
      <p class="problem-sub reveal">
        By then the lead has messaged three competitors and bought from whoever replied first.
        You didn't lose the sale on price or product — you lost it on silence. DMClosed answers
        in seconds, every time, on every channel.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-panel reveal">
      <span class="panel-tag">Speed to first reply</span>
      <div class="problem-bars" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="bar">
          <span class="bar-label">You, replying by hand</span>
          <span class="bar-track"><span class="bar-fill bar-slow" data-bar></span></span>
          <span class="bar-val">~14 hrs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bar">
          <span class="bar-label">DMClosed</span>
          <span class="bar-track"><span class="bar-fill bar-fast" data-bar></span></span>
          <span class="bar-val">4 sec</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="panel-note">Leads are <strong>21×</strong> more likely to convert when you reply in the first 5 minutes. DMClosed never misses that window.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 1rem + 4vw, 4.5rem); align-items: center;
  }
  .problem-h { font-size: var(--step-3); line-height: 1.04; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
  .problem .kicker { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .problem-h .big {
    display: inline-block; font-size: var(--step-5); color: var(--primary-hi);
    line-height: 0.9; margin-right: 0.3rem; vertical-align: -0.06em;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  html.has-motion .problem-h .big {
    transform: scale(0.9); transform-origin: left bottom;
    transition: transform 1.1s var(--ease-out-quint);
  }
  html.has-motion .problem-h.is-in .big { transform: scale(1); }
  .problem-sub { font-size: var(--step-1); color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 46ch; }

  .problem-panel {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-2), var(--surface));
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(1.4rem, 1rem + 1.5vw, 2.2rem);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .panel-tag { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
  .problem-bars { display: grid; gap: 1.1rem; margin: 1.2rem 0 1.3rem; }
  .bar { display: grid; gap: 0.45rem; }
  .bar-label { font-size: var(--step--1); color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 500; }
  .bar-track { height: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-pill); background: var(--bg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
  .bar-fill { display: block; height: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius-pill); width: 0; }
  .bar-slow { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--surface-hi), var(--muted)); }
  .bar-fast { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ember), var(--primary), var(--accent)); box-shadow: 0 0 18px -2px var(--glow-amber); }
  .bar-val { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--step-1); }
  .bar:first-child .bar-val { color: var(--muted); }
  .bar:last-child .bar-val { color: var(--accent-hi); }
  .panel-note { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
  .panel-note strong { color: var(--primary-hi); font-weight: 700; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .problem-sub { max-width: 56ch; }
  }
</style>
